The file is a minimal Express application with two endpoints (`/health` and `/users`) that return static JSON. **There is no database access, no user input processing, no authentication logic, no file I/O, and no templating.** Most OWASP Top 10 categories simply do not apply to this code as written. Below I flag only issues actually grounded in the file, plus forward-looking concerns for when the app grows.

