## Findings

### Medium severity

1. **No security headers / `helmet` middleware** — Missing `X-Content-Type-Options`, `X-Frame-Options`, `Strict-Transport-Security`, CSP, etc. Add `app.use(helmet())`.

2. **PII exposure without auth on `/users`** (line 11–16) — Returns email addresses with no authentication, authorization, or rate limiting. Even with seed data today, this endpoint shape invites real PII to be dropped in later. Add authn/authz middleware before it becomes a real leak.

