4. **Listens on all interfaces** (line 18) — `app.listen(3000, ...)` binds `0.0.0.0` by default. In dev/container environments this can expose the service unexpectedly. Prefer `app.listen(3000, '127.0.0.1', ...)` unless external access is intentional.

