2. **No security headers** — `helmet` is not installed/applied. The app will respond without `Content-Security-Policy`, `X-Frame-Options`, `Strict-Transport-Security`, `X-Content-Type-Options`, etc. Add `app.use(helmet())` early in the middleware chain.

